replies.body: Hi I have had similar errors, just replugging the lighting schedule might do the trick or try internalize data on the lighting schedule. that worked for me. I dont know if internalize data works for string-text inputs always, meaning when you open the definition next time, so you might have to do it again each time when you open the definition. I havent looked at your definition yet but.
